v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>packages used by standard</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/eslint\">eslint</a></strong> - AST-based pattern checker for JavaScript</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/standard-engine\">standard-engine</a></strong> - standard's guts, extracted into a reuseable package. build your own!</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/eslint-config-standard\">eslint-config-standard</a></strong> - standard eslint rules, as a shareable config</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/eslint-config-standard-jsx\">eslint-config-standard-jsx</a></strong> - standard eslint rules for JSX</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/eslint-plugin-standard\">eslint-plugin-standard</a></strong> - standard custom eslint rules (not part of eslint core)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"automatic-code-formatters\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#automatic-code-formatters\" aria-label=\"automatic code formatters permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>automatic code formatters</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">standard --fix</code> - automatic formatting is built-in to <code class=\"language-text\">standard</code>!</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/prettier-standard\">prettier-standard</a></strong> - format with <a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier\">prettier</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">39.6k</span></span></a> configured to standard rules</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/watson/453fc63cace521fcdadc\">\"unix commands\" gist</a></strong> - A list of search and replace unix commands to help make a node repository 'standard' compliant</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"editor-plugins\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#editor-plugins\" aria-label=\"editor plugins permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>editor plugins</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Every major text editor has a plugin or built-in support for <code class=\"language-text\">standard</code>. See the <a href=\"https://github.com/standard/standard#are-there-text-editor-plugins\">full list</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/standard/standard#are-there-text-editor-plugins\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">25.5k</span></span></a> of supported editors.</li>\n<li>Atom: <strong><a href=\"https://atom.io/packages/linter-js-standard\">linter-js-standard</a></strong> - linter</li>\n<li>Atom: <strong><a href=\"https://atom.io/packages/linter-js-standard-engine\">linter-js-standard-engine</a></strong> - linter</li>\n<li>Atom: <strong><a href=\"https://atom.io/packages/standard-formatter\">standard-formatter</a></strong> - auto-fixer</li>\n<li>Atom: <strong><a href=\"https://atom.io/packages/standardjs-snippets\">standardjs-snippets</a></strong> - code snippets</li>\n<li>Brackets: <strong><a href=\"https://github.com/ishamf/brackets-standard/\">brackets-standard</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/ishamf/brackets-standard/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">11</span></span></a></strong> - linter</li>\n<li>Emacs: see <a href=\"https://github.com/standard/standard#emacs\">readme</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/standard/standard#emacs\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">25.5k</span></span></a></li>\n<li>Sublime Text: <strong><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/SublimeLinter-contrib-standard\">SublimeLinter-contrib-standard</a></strong> - linter</li>\n<li>Sublime Text: <strong><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/StandardFormat\">StandardFormat</a></strong> - auto-fixer</li>\n<li>Visual Studio Code: <strong><a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=standard.vscode-standard\">vscode-standard</a></strong> - linter &#x26; auto-fixer</li>\n<li>Vim: see <a href=\"https://github.com/standard/standard#vim\">readme</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/standard/standard#vim\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">25.5k</span></span></a></li>\n<li>Visual Studio Code: <strong><a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=capaj.vscode-standardjs-snippets\">vscode-standardjs-snippets</a></strong> - code snippets</li>\n<li>Visual Studio Code: <strong><a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=TimonVS.ReactSnippetsStandard\">vscode-react-standard</a></strong> - code snippets</li>\n<li>WebStorm (PhpStorm, IntelliJ, RubyMine, JetBrains, etc.): built-in support. see <a href=\"https://github.com/standard/standard#webstorm-phpstorm-intellij-rubymine-jetbrains-etc\">readme</a><a data-role=